wspan="1" colspan="1">Australasia</td><td valign="top" align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">31 (26.7)</td></tr><tr><td valign="top" align="left" scope="row" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Europe<hr /></td><td valign="top" align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">7 (6.1)<hr /></td></tr><tr><td valign="top" align="left" scope="col" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Duration of travel, h</td><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"></td></tr><tr><td valign="top" align="left" scope="row" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x0003c;3</td><td valign="top" align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">22 (19.0)</td></tr><tr><td valign="top" align="left" scope="row" rowspan="1" colspan="1">3&#x02013;5.9</td><td valign="top" align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">34 (29.3)</td></tr><tr><td valign="top" align="left" scope="row" rowspan="1" colspan="1">6&#x02013;14.9</td><td valign="top" align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">36 (31.0)</td></tr><tr><td valign="top" align="left" scope="row" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><span class="underline">&#x0003e;</span>15<hr /></td><td valign="top" align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">24 (20.7)<hr /></td></tr><tr><td valign="top" align="left" scope="col" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Onset of symptoms</td><td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"></td></tr><tr><td valign="top" align="left" scope="row" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Before embarkation</td><td valign="top" align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">29 (25.0)</td></tr><tr><td valign="top" align="left" scope="row" rowspan="1" colspan="1">While travelling</td><td valign="top" align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">17 (14.7)</td></tr><tr><td valign="top" align="left" scope="row" rowspan="1" colspan="1">After disembarkation<hr /></td><td valign="top" align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">70 (60.3)<hr /></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" valign="top" align="left" scope="col" rowspan="1">Source of referral to TTSH screening center</td></tr><tr><td valign="top" align="left" scope="row" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Airpo